> @alex2wong I want custom dynamic text at center.

sure, the label could be customized by string formatter or callback function based on data 

```
label: {
    normal: {
        show: false,
        position: 'center',
        formatter: function(params) {  // callback function 
                        if (params.dataIndex === 0) {
                            return params.data[params.dataIndex];
                        } else { return '' }
                    }
    },
    emphasis: {
        show: true,
        formatter: `customized {a}\n {b}: {c}`  // string formatter
    }
},
```

please refer to doc: https://echarts.apache.org/en/option.html#series-pie.label.formatter 
and try in this demo: https://echarts.apache.org/examples/zh/editor.html?c=pie-doughnut

您好，那我详细讲一个方法吧。
1.进入echarts官网，选择树图的最后一个实例
2.在示例代码中插入window.myChart=myChart以便控制台可以直接引用
3.将以下代码复制进控制台中
var testData = [
    { "name": "3", "children": [] },
    { "name": "3", "children": [{ "name": "2", "children": [] }, { "name": "" }] },
    { "name": "2", "children": [{ "name": "1", "children": [] }, { "name": "3", "children": [] }] },
    { "name": "2", "children": [{ "name": "1", "children": [] }, { "name": "3", "children": [{ "name": "" }, { "name": "4", "children": [] }] }] },
];
testData.forEach((data, index) => {
    setTimeout(() => {
        option.series[0].data = [data];
        myChart.setOption(option);
    }, (index + 1) * 1000);
});

